			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I got them from the first camp (as your walking towards Dulak) on the left. Its know as the fort. I was able to med/prepare in a corner where no mobs are. The trolls seem not to aggro unless your right on top of them at Lvl 53. I made pet guard near that corner and then went to work... The strongest form of Malaise you have at your level should allow you to safely pull 1 mob at a time. So, hit them with Mailosi, then run to your pet. You will either get hit by a spell or hit by melee on the way (in which case your pet will attack), or you will make it to your pet and order him to attack while on the run. When you turn around, your pet should be beating profusely on your target. Kill it, med if necessary, repeat.
<br />

<br />
The drops come very slow. I got 2 Seas in 45 mins.... no lava yet. Total time there is 2 hours now. The spawn rate seems to be about 15 mins. Ill be camping them again my next session. Good Luck.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
